#
# amidst CLI surface (decoded from @Option fields
# in CommandLineParameters.java):
#   -mcpath <directory>     location of the '.minecraft' directory
#   -mcjar <file>           Minecraft jar (depends -mcjson, forbids -profile)
#   -mcjson <file>          Minecraft json (depends -mcjar, forbids -profile)
#   -profile <name>         profile name (forbids -mcjar/-mcjson)
#   -biome-profiles <dir>   biome profile directory
#   -history <file>         seed history file
#   -log <file>             log file path
#   -seed <string>          initial seed (custom SeedHandler)
#   -world-type <string>    world type (depends -seed, custom WorldTypeHandler)
#   -help                   print usage information
#   -version                print version
#
# amidst is the Advanced Minecraft Interface and
# Data/Structure Tracker — visualizes Minecraft
# world generation (biomes, structures, slime
# chunks, stronghold positions) for any seed and
# world type without actually generating chunks.
# Authored by toolbox4minecraft (founder: Skidam).
# 2264 GH stars.  Sister tools: chunkbase tools
# (web-based seed mapping), MCASelector (chunk
# selector), seedfinder/mcseedfinder/cubitec
# tools.
